  <brief_title>A Prospective, Single Arm, Multi-Center Clinical Study in Collaboration With the Interagency Registry for Mechanically Assisted Circulatory Support (INTERMACS®) to Evaluate the Thoracotomy Implant Technique of the HeartWare HVAD® System in Patients With Advanced Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <acronym>HVAD LATERAL</acronym>
